data.description: SELLER OFFERING 10k in closing costs or rate buy down with acceptable offer. Welcome to this gorgeous DR Horton “Kiawa” floor plan nestled in Harker Heights desired Cedarbrook Subdivision.  This home boasts five large bedrooms, three full bathrooms, a private office and a three-car garage. The open concept living area and kitchen is a entertainers dream. There is a bedroom downstairs with its own full bathroom. Upstairs is the master bedroom, plus three other bedrooms, a large loft area and a built in desk. All the closets upstairs are HUGE! New St Augustine grass has just been laid down in both the front and backyard. PLUS the home has solar panels that will be paid off at closing by the seller's! This subdivision is amazing with a community pool and playground. Come check out this beautiful home!
